snippet.title: Movod II: The Resurrection (1992, Macintosh) - Test Recording [720p]
snippet.description:
MovoD = Macintosh-operated vehicles of Destruction.

Created by Tony Small [https://www.youtube.com/user/tonysmallsss]

You shoot at your opponent's tank until it explodes!

Tournament mode - https://youtu.be/nk5cd3yCUMM
